Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't coming\nback anymore, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you ask Kagome for forgiveness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:59.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how those two made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:03.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... probably Kagome gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:04.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, she forgave Inuyasha's\nindiscretion with Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can she endure it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha was quite depressed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess she didn't want\nto back him into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he's usually in some tight spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems to be repenting just a bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where Naraku's castle\nused to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Traces of Naraku's miasma still remain.\NSo there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... there's nary\na hint of the remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was Naraku's castle really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you think about it, we've been\nlured to a fake castle before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was what we saw just an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:21.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:29.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.\NNaraku's castle was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Sango, what's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up? Found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father's armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That day, we slayers were\nlured to Naraku's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiraikotsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And my father\nand all the others were slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were killed by\nmy younger brother, Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His mind was being\ncontrolled by Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Their bodies were buried\nin the corner of the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must not leave your father\nand the others in this tainted ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will find another burial ground\nfor them and offer prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is where Naraku's castle was...\NBut what of its occupants?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango's brother, Kohaku...\nwho was controlled by Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he perish with the castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, at least, wild dogs\nwon't dig up their graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let this be\nyour resting place for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:53.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someday, I promise to erect\nproper graves for you in our village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The village is abandoned now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kohaku and I are still alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we both watch over the graves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kohaku{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid, you're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've totally entertained us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:43.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of which,\nyou helped cut firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be tired.\NCome inside and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Did you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-uh... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or at least your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,used to live close to the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About ten days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Hitomi's castle\nsuddenly disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we found you unconscious\nthe next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe something terribly\nfrightening happened to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you lost your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, never mind.\NNo need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:40.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Just stay as long\nas you like, until you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:43.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, there's lot more. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Castle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a feeling I was there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gramps! Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, so don't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! I remember!\NI ran away from the castle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night...\nwhen the castle disappeared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:41.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, keeping you alive\nis no longer necessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can join your father\nand the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's near! Beyond this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! So are they after the\NSacred Jewel fragment, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:28.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, you can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, obey and return the Sacred\NJewel fragment in your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sacred Jewel fragment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand over the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demon is trying to get\nthe fragment in Kohaku's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel fragment\nin Kohaku's back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is his lifeline.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the fragment is removed, he'll die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were under Naraku's mind control...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and you were in Naraku's castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why are you... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've hurt your arm. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:56.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku... You really\ndon't remember anything about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,before you escaped from the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even about Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:13.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keeping you alive\nis no longer necessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Join your father and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could that have been...Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like it!\NThat kid is just putting on an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the Kohaku\nwho appeared before us that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was like a puppet...\na human without a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it safe to leave them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango wanted it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The slayers' village?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... that's where we used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then was I also a demon slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rest a bit.\NWe have lots of work ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, be prepared, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're eleven years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time you got some\nreal experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:27.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:30.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do demons really spit fire\nand poison?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, are you afraid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}N- no such thing! But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We only slay oversized\nsnakes and spiders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father always says...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the demons to fear most\nare the ones pretending to be humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If such demons\nget ahold of Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}it'll be terrible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:09.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then that day\nwhen we were summoned by Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that was Kohaku's\nvery first battle experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel so empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just like the Kohaku of old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quiet...and a bit cowardly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just try to remember little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be together from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you so shy for?\NWe're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:14:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku has come back to me.\NHe's escaped from Naraku's grasp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I want to believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give 'im a couple of knocks\nand he'll show his real self!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whether it's a trap or not,\nher dear brother is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:32.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... if this is a trap,\NSango will be so hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:36.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku loves to play\nwith people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you won't tell her, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-wait! Stop, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About Kohaku...\NThis has to be Naraku's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I believe in Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Naraku's aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else can I do\nexcept to trust him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a trick Naraku is likely to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we hadn't come to his aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,his Sacred Jewel fragment\nwould have been removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he would really have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen... that's the trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel as though that kind woman will\nbecome unhappy...all because of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must not stay here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're being blinded by love\nfor your kid brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A huge number of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His advance guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're... not after Kohaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:29.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I sense\nthe Sacred Jewel fragment moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sango!\NWe must protect Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura! Whaddya want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hiding Kohaku, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't act innocent!\NThe kid Naraku's kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:10.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku ran off\namidst the confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with the Sacred Jewel fragment\nin his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why you've come for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku always goes overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because he wants the fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he sends out this army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're after\nthe Sacred Jewel fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... although once that's removed,\NKohaku will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're under orders\nto let Sango have him after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-why... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:39.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why go through all this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're my... brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're my one and only little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, watch Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll stop those demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku! You must live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- If this keeps up...\N- Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm out of arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll hide in that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll wait until Inuyasha comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:35.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Sango is really strong.\NDon't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:45.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku... You still don't remember?\NThat Sango is your older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she... She seems so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango had always worried about you\nwhile you two were apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's always so cheerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but once in a while,\nshe looks very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'm glad that you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it... Is it okay to stay with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you'll start to remember\nabout Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to remember...\nabout her and everything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...what's this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel scared...\nsomething I don't want to remember...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill her... Kill Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... He's so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:51.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all out of Sacred Arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:50.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, who has lost his memory,\nis still being controlled by Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is about to carry out\NNaraku's order: "Kill Kagome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:24:00.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango finds out and resolves to\nkill Kohaku, then herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku realizes the trap\nand uses his Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to suck in the demons,\npoison insects and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must stop Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"That Unforgettable Face!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
